The aroma of coffee and catered snacks wafts from the lounge, while camera crews from the university media team capture interviews on-site. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and consulting firms have stacked glossy case study booklets on high tables, further enriching the event's offerings. Additionally, career counselors are present, advising attendees to maintain eye contact.
